2021-03-15T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"捉鬼大師？<br />\n<br />\n扣帽子，又名貼標籤、咒罵法、鬥臭法、井裏下毒（英語：Poisoning the Well），是一種非常常見的政治宣傳與修辭手法，也是一種典型的人身攻擊，讓閱聽人在還無法深入了解、思考之前，就率先被某人身上負面的標籤所影響，使閱聽人對其事有種「先入為主」的負面認知與不良的刻板印象。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，你呢度係轉移視線去我身上，從而迴避你嘅雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n紅鯡魚（Red Herring）是英文熟語。指以修辭或文學的手法轉移議題焦點與注意力，是一種政治宣傳、公關及戲劇創作的技巧，也是一種邏輯謬誤。"},{"pid":"339b26d63aab0c2d7596a4970a3e373e0c353bb2","tid":2438550,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a23c78b6fb60decd40f653bac338d520d2a2d0a","tid":2438550,"uid":25059,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"db2f2d256a648af3524a0e77c5a71c5e25af194d","tid":2438550,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddc6b124b27f37151a8b83fd3a349bfaddefdb5","tid":2438550,"uid":238660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"你個歷史台同熱狗d衛星 channel 好 fd 下"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"又想老屈人地係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"我冇話人鬼，我淨係話人 fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccca793f8bb2ca63819fcf4aefde2faa9a383c52","tid":2438550,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db2f2d256a648af3524a0e77c5a71c5e25af194d","tid":2438550,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eddc6b124b27f37151a8b83fd3a349bfaddefdb5","tid":2438550,"uid":238660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"你個歷史台同熱狗d衛星 channel 好 fd 下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68c5a35f8341ca7607b623e6849c7e36a801747","tid":24385